{"id":120388,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/11/简讯：广州取消亚运免费乘车措施/","date":"2010-11-07T12:05:21Z","modified":"2010-11-07T12:05:21Z","title":"简讯：广州取消亚运免费乘车措施","content":"<div>\n<p>中国广州市宣布，取消原定在举办亚运会期间实施的公共交通免费措施。</p>\n<p>广州市交通部门负责人说，有关措施自11月1日起实施以来，广州的巴士和地铁都出现了超负荷现象。</p>\n<p>有关措施原定在亚运会与亚残运会期间合共实施30个工作日。</p>\n<p>现在广州市政府将改为提供现金交通补贴。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/JpYOTqHWZh_mznQcbOXO6NvDur4/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/JpYOTqHWZh_mznQcbOXO6NvDur4/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/JpYOTqHWZh_mznQcbOXO6NvDur4/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/JpYOTqHWZh_mznQcbOXO6NvDur4/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=K374bMFB6co:5Cxv2niuYew:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/K374bMFB6co\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/s